---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="About Us">
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 class="section-title" style="margin-bottom: 48px;">About WellnessLiving</h1>
      <div class="about-content">
        <p>WellnessLiving is a leading all-in-one business management platform designed specifically for the fitness, wellness, and beauty industries. We help thousands of businesses streamline operations, engage clients, and grow revenue.</p>

        <p>Founded with a mission to democratize technology for small and medium wellness businesses, we combine powerful scheduling, payment processing, marketing automation, and AI-driven analytics into a single, easy-to-use platform.</p>

        <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Our Mission</h2>
        <p>To empower every wellness business — from yoga studios and gyms to spas and salons — with the same enterprise-grade tools that were previously only available to large chains. We believe technology should be an enabler, not a barrier.</p>

        <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Why Choose Us</h2>
        <ul style="padding-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
          <li><strong>All-in-One Platform</strong> — No more juggling multiple tools. Everything from booking to billing in one place.</li>
          <li><strong>AI-Powered Insights</strong> — Predictive analytics help you make smarter decisions about pricing, staffing, and retention.</li>
          <li><strong>White-Label Mobile App</strong> — Your brand, your app, your clients' pocket.</li>
          <li><strong>24/7 Support</strong> — Dedicated team ready to help whenever you need it.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Our Team</h2>
        <p>We're a passionate team of engineers, designers, and wellness industry experts based across North America. We use our own platform every day and obsess over making it better for our customers.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Want to Learn More?</h2>
      <p>Get in touch and see how WellnessLiving can help your business thrive.</p>
      <a href="#" class="btn">Contact Us</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
